name: Vul Tazaene
Lore: 'Security officer from Kiffex searching for the Tonnika sisters. In love with one of them, he''s not sure which.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Twice during battle at same system, may use 2 Force to add 2 to any destiny of 2. If present with Tonnika Sisters, Vul and Tonnika Sisters are lost.',
